                "name": "Before Combat",
                "text": "The wizard casts <i>bear\u2019s endurance</i>, <i>mage armor</i>, and <i>protection from energy </i>(fire)."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "tactic",
                "name": "During Combat",
                "text": "The wizard casts <i>greater invisibility</i>, then uses <i>transmute rock to mud </i>to trap foes. He casts area damage spells at trapped targets and uses <i>stinking cloud </i>and <i>resilient sphere </i>to hinder those who escape the mud."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "tactic",
                "name": "Base Statistics",
                "text": "Without <i>bear\u2019s endurance</i>, <i>mage armor</i>, and <i>protection from energy </i>(fire), the wizard\u2019s statistics are <b>AC </b>11, touch 10, flat-footed 11; <b>hp </b>74; <b>Fort </b>+6; <b>Immune </b>none; <b>Con </b>16."
